Zain Board to Discuss Zain Saudi Restructuring, Al-Jarida Says

-- B y   D a h l i a   K h o l a i f
-- 
2011-03-13T06:01:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-13/zain-board-to-discuss-zain-saudi-restructuring-al-jarida-says.html
Board of Mobile Telecommunications
Co., also known as Zain, will meet today to discuss plans to
restructure its Saudi Arabian unit "if it doesn’t get sold,"  Al-
Jarida  reported, without saying where it got the information.  The board will also discuss plans for the unit’s $2.6
billion of debt, according to the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dahlia Kholaif in Kuwait at 
 dkholaif@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
